---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="End User Licence Agreement | Viewpo"
  description="End User Licence Agreement for the Viewpo integration for Vercel. Covers licence scope, data handling, warranty, and liability."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">End User Licence Agreement</h1>
        <p class="text-foreground/50 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: February 2026</p>

        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          By installing or using the Viewpo integration for Vercel, you agree to these terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">1. Licence</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Viewpo grants you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable licence to use this integration to connect your Vercel account with the Viewpo application.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">2. Scope</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This integration accesses your Vercel projects and deployments in read-only mode. It does not modify, delete, or create any resources in your Vercel account.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">3. Data</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Authentication tokens are stored encrypted on Viewpo's servers (Supabase Vault). No Vercel credentials are stored on your device.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">4. No warranty</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This integration is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">5. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Viewpo shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of this integration.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">6. Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We may update these terms at any time. Continued use constitutes acceptance.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading font-semibold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Questions about this agreement? Email us at <a href="mailto:support@viewpo.io" class="text-links hover:text-primary transition-colors">support@viewpo.io</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
